SMS,Ingenuity,SMSi,is,an,SMS,marketing,service,that,can,be,used,for,bulk,messaging,birthday,reminders,timed,campaigns,one,on,one,communications,text,to,vote,campaigns,and,recurring,messages,SMSi,comes,with,features,for,automatically,personalizing,messages,managing,contacts,and,creating,message,templates,Developers,can,integrate,the,SMSi,messaging,gateway,into,their,own,application,using,the,SMSi,API,This,allows,them,to,send,SMS,programmatically,using,a,wide,variety,of,protocols,and,methods